text: Ferdinand Daniš (born 7 January 1929) is a Czech gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics, the 1956 Summer Olympics and the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lučenec
